{"id":"18b12c31-571f-4a16-b0ce-e7596aec5dec","name":"Fate/𝐑𝐏𝐆 - 𝕃𝕚𝕞𝕚𝕥𝕝𝕖𝕤𝕤 ℂ𝕠𝕕𝕖𝕤","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/j-wtzKQGTzOMlaAFiDAHb.gif\" alt=\"Banner.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"I ask of you, are you my Master?\"</em></strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ef5cd8d7-763f-460e-91c5-511c1f8dd994_character-servant-ver-fate-𝐑-𝐏-𝐆-𝕃-𝕚-𝕞-𝕚-𝕥-𝕝-𝕖-𝕤-𝕤-ℂ-𝕠-𝕕-𝕖-𝕤\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXk02qfdFd5834NHCYjTi.webp\" alt=\"Banner.webp\"></a></p><hr><ul><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/scripts/7ef92bc0-acdf-4d2e-9ee4-1cf9c716b388\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Fate/RPG Servant Lorebook (Servants + Keywords)</strong></a></p><p>NOTE: If the Link doesn't go through, simply click on the Script \"Fate - Servants [CLICK HERE]\"</p></li></ul><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JUcwdMTNvJbI2KjkiHjwT.webp\" alt=\"Chess.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">『<em>The </em><strong><em>Holy Grail</em></strong><em>, a relic with mystical powers beyond human understanding that can grant any wish. For centuries, countless mages have fought to possess the Holy Grail. This conflict became known as the </em><strong><em>Holy Grail War</em></strong><em>. Seven Masters and seven heroic spirits, known as Servants, engage in a battle hidden from the eyes of ordinary people. </em><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Only the last Master standing shall claim the Grail</em></strong></span><em>.</em>』</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(57, 0, 108); color: inherit;\">IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER</mark></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"zReHs\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esr